io.github.whippetdb.memory.api

Interface MemDataIO

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MemIO
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    MemDataArray, MemDataBuffer, MemDataSpace
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AlignedVarData, DbFile, DirectDataIO, DynamicDataIO, HeapDataIO, HybridKeyWrapper, HybridKeyWrapperOld, ProxyDataArray, ProxyDataIO, SimpleDirectDataBuffer, SimpleDirectDataIO, SimpleDirectDataSpace, SimpleFileDataBuffer, SimpleFileDataIO, SimpleFileDataSpace, SimpleHeapDataBuffer, SimpleHeapDataIO, SimpleHeapDataSpace, SimpleJournalingDataIO, SimpleJournalingMemSpace, SimpleLog, StringWrapper, VarData

    public interface MemDataIO
extends MemIO
    MemIO with added methods for integer types. It is byte order-aware. Default implementaions are slow, implementations should override.
